-*-Text-*-

		       	      ==========================
			            RYOUREADY RELEASE VERSIONS 
		       	      ==========================

Version 0.4 (opened November 30, 2014) --------------------------   
  * qqnorm_spss: SPSS like qqplots

Version 0.3 (November 30, 2014) --------------------------   
  * count_na: count the number of NAs per row or column of a dataframe or matrix
  * collapse_responseset: convert a multiple response set with sereval
variables into one variable
  * recode2: recode several variables in a dataframe at once supplying the column indexes
or names


Version 0.2 (December 15, 2013) --------------------------   
  
  * intervals: converts standard mathematical interval notation to a definition as required by the recode function from the car package


Version 0.1 (June 13, 2013) --------------------------   

	* Association measures for nominal and ordinal data tables: nom.lambda
    nom.uncertainty, ord.gamma, ord.somers.d, ord.tau
  * Dataset NGO added
